HE is known for speaking his mind and of course having a child with Dj Zinhle, but there’s no doubt that his music is loved in Mzansi. So, it’s no surprise that so early in the year, Kiernan Forbes, better known as AKA has something to celebrate, as he is set to achieve a feat that no other artist has managed to do. His beef with Cassper might not be over, but AKA is certainly popping some champas after taking to his Twitter account to announce his latest achievement. The rapper wrote: “It gives me great pleasure to announce my concert at the Sun Arena on the 17th of March LIVE with a 30 piece Orchestra. and band. I believe now, with 3 classic solo albums done and dusted, the time is right. #AKAOrchestraOnTheSquare  